<p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--ink-light);margin-top:-.3rem;">Editorial scores reflect our own assessment based on the research described in this article — not a certification, lab test, or audited rating.</p>

<p>OLSP Academy offers a genuinely low-friction entry point into affiliate marketing, with structured training and an active community. The honest caveat is that it is, at its core, a recruitment-driven commission system: most realistic earnings come from referrals upgrading inside the ecosystem, not from selling outside products. Treat any income figures you see — including the ones cited in this article — as unverified self-reports, not evidence of typical results. If you join, do so as a low-cost experiment in learning affiliate marketing, not as a guaranteed income source.</p>

